Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:06.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,与步行侠的对决后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「幸存者」的各位都暂时瘫倒在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不只是身体上遭受了创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,内心也或多或少有心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:22.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人类太闲的时候就会不自主地胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想那些因匆忙而忘记的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想那些刻意不愿想起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都会再度占据脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人类这东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:42.52,renleiyongzhe note1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(785.2,856)}{\fade(500,500)\pos(690.8,841.6)}冒险者还没能拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我们接下来要去什么样的城市  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是好久没去的迷宫都市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你还记得阿尔卡斯叔叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,他摸过我的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,又能见到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:07.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈都爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:19.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:25.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了  阿尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:20.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「粘水关」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最低等级的冒险者首先要从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,从今天起我也是冒险者了吧  阿尔卡斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:33.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,还有成为冒险者之后就不要叫我「先生」了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,冒险者间没有上下之分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,听好了  尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,冒险者之间就是要信任彼此相互协助…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.35,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,啊  它在吃草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,太大意的话小心被偷袭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦  阿尔卡斯先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这就叫大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然我成为冒险者是为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但也有想过如果那时自己有力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,说不定能和父亲母亲一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,加入「武艺百般」时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.68,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,阿尔卡斯给了我一把短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最让我开心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:40.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,他是考虑到我的资质才选给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这都是些陈年旧事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我的过去已经被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,并作为现在的我的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  我也没有觉得后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要是那时候那样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要是那时候这样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我给了阿尔卡斯不同的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我现在会不会还在「武艺百般」中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果那时我没逃走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,会不会和父亲母亲一起死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不过只看头顶就能认出来真不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,麻烦了啊  看起来雨不会那么快停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我还在头疼怎么把伞还给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这样说的话你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,说起来  我还没问过你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我只是个喜欢偶像的野狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我也只是个偶像的阿加特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那天也下着雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看到野狗先生在雨中都不打伞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,下意识地就跟你聊起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但知道野狗先生也有自己的家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,说起来  之前我们事务所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:58.49,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,打断一下  你要在这种状态聊很久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,给你带来麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  说不上是麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那就再聊一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,说不定就是因为有那天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我才得到了救赎也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,难道说  野狗先生是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不时会有幻听的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,烦捏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:32.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,还要这样站着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.38,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,至雨止时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.38,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,杀死纳尔迦瓦医生的人是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:07.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:09.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:11.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我赢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你要的是纳尔迦瓦医生的继承权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哪有人为了打赌断三根肋骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你根本不懂啊  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我输了的话又有三根要断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,赢了的话你那三根能恢复得快点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可能发生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.66,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这医生脑子没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:45.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,治疗是个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然很微不足道  但能帮到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在治疗时不用想多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:55.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不可思议的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,步行侠纳尔迦瓦先生如此劣迹斑斑应当憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:04.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,现在的我却无法憎恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,像是继承他的道路似的模仿他的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是在追悼吗  亦或是自我满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  这两者或许是同一种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:19.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:31.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好几次我反复从梦中惊醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,以些许的救赎为饵食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.85,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今日的我仍旧被苦恼折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人生真是如此残酷之物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,昨日已过而今日犹存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,向目光可及处前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人类是否真的无法得到回报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,赌博这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在没有赢钱的直觉的时候就不该下注
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然我提不起兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但为了找回日常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这些天我都在模仿着从前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多么奢侈的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我对这样的生活没什么不满
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:45.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,现在  应该也没有人会骗我或拖我的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,生活顺心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:49.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我还能有什么不满的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:50.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,胜负相当收支均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:00.88,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这样太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡兰有没有尝过这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:26.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大伙过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,马马虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你还在坚持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,约好了不干涉他人的隐私的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然步行侠事件中有让人伤心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但最后也达到了计划中的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我们必须接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这恰如其分的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  现在大家之间却有了层无形的障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:13.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看起来似乎都在与某种东西斗争着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,幸存者三条款  其一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,绝不干涉他人的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你说什么都没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.49,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你这种人真这么想就是白费口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:44.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,居然在这么危险的地方行医
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎么看都需要我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,就当我是保镖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:05.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这不是新一期的月刊利莫里亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,奥莉薇娅还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,让我看看写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,游走于迷宫都市有意思的怪人前100名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:23.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已经吃过早饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,呃  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我一整晚都在打包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已经在雷德先生那吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我抽两口就当早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:46.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  那我先去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,难道大家都已经释怀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:06.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我以前的队长  卡里欧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那个我曾经宣誓效忠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,却背叛了我  抛弃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,还把我所有的东西都偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽说他欺骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但在「白鹭」的日子我其实过得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是  卡里欧斯偷走了我族群的宝物「龙王宝珠」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这件事是决不能被原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我从没有忘记这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小妹妹你是虎人族东西得轻拿轻放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎么会  我什么都没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,无心之举确实没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,可装傻可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  我真的没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽说你看上去是刚从乡下来不久的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但在这「迷宫都市」可不能就这么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你是要用半价1万底拿买下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.88,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要确认下这女孩的爪痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:13.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,听说大伙在准备「夏眠祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,想着过去瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「夏眠祭」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,写作在夏天中入眠  所以叫「夏眠祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:34.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,听说在这个季节魔物的活动也会弱化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,能吃到好东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那应该是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那可真让人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那么耀眼的光芒有将一日也会消失得无影无踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,消失的话  是好事还是坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是觉得当下越是重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,相对的  过去就会渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  珍重仍留存下来的东西那就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果是的话  我想只留下我喜欢的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,高傲的龙人族有着一项使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:19.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那就是协助能成为勇者的人类拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是龙人族椿氏族族长的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡兰椿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,寄宿了火龙之加护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一名高傲的龙战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,奥莉薇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好了  是号外哦  号外号外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是月刊利莫里亚的特别号外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你在吵什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  不得了了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的是个大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看起来确实很不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不得了得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,到底是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,现在怎么还能这么平静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,情绪不再高涨点我可不说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什什什什么  到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不错哦  不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我很讨厌这种煽动行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,其实啊  居然有这么一回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:22.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,特报  发现了传说中的暗黑魔人复活征兆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,的传闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我说  别在我之前爆出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.77,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不是你自己把这篇报道撒得周围都是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,又是假新闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:35.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,老是说点没边的东西  以后没人信你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但——是呢  这次我的信源是杠杠的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什么  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不愧是绊  眼光就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你别当真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我说「白色假面」也牵扯其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:52.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:55.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,这点倒还不能确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果我说搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,流通「幻王宝珠」的黑市所在地了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:03.64,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你搞清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:04.85,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,现在还没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然我现在还没搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但把那些可疑的点连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:14.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,并写出吊人胃口的新闻就是我的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,牵强附会的东西可不算新闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都说无风不起浪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如果没有风就让八卦杂志掀起浪花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始你就在说自己在编大话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,编大话？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不不  麻烦你说这是浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是浪漫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是浪漫哦  绊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,听起来真令人雀跃啊  浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「龙王宝珠」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,也会流进你说的那个黑市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:42.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,卡兰小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:49.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,说实在  我确实不该执着于卡里欧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:54.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  我不知道我该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.62,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,虽然跟大家一起的日子很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但我也感觉到自己在对什么事情视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有着放不下的东西  那么抓住就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,只是  你这次可不是一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,像步行侠那次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我们一起行动就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有什么问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我们是「幸存者」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:30.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,无论我们要跟谁做对手  都一定要活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,纳尔迦瓦和「白色假面」之间的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,某种程度上是事先就能看出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,而关于更深层的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我也经常有听说一些流言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,坏人的背后会牵扯到好人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,恶的背后连接的是更大的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,坏人们背后的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,找到最深处的那个头头  然后打飞他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,事情开始有趣起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你完完全全上了她的贼船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那我们就干这一笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都说到这份上了定得惩奸除恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:00.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克  我也想一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,全员一致  让我们一起打倒传说中的魔神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,加了个油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,算了  就这样吧
